or the new year will be handled according to the `clip` behavior.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/ZonedDateTime.html#Std.Time.ZonedDateTime.withYearClip\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">ZonedDateTime</span>.<span class=\"name\">withYearClip</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">dt</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/ZonedDateTime.html#Std.Time.ZonedDateTime\">ZonedDateTime</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">year</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/Date/Unit/Year.html#Std.Time.Year.Offset\">Year.Offset</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/ZonedDateTime.html#Std.Time.ZonedDateTime\">ZonedDateTime</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Std/Time/Zoned/ZonedDateTime.lean#L452-L459","name":"Std.Time.ZonedDateTime.withMonthRollOver","line":452,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Std/Time/Zoned/ZonedDateTime.html#Std.Time.ZonedDateTime.withMonthRollOver","doc":"Creates a new `ZonedDateTime` by adjusting the month to the given `month` value.\nThe day is rolled over to the next valid month if necessary.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/ZonedDateTime.html#Std.Time.ZonedDateTime.withMonthRollOver\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">ZonedDateTime</span>.<span class=\"name\">withMonthRollOver</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">dt</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/ZonedDateTime.html#Std.Time.ZonedDateTime\">ZonedDateTime</a>)</span></span>\n<span cla